}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "YNY00A-1.6" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. This same P/N is found on the [[SerComm IP1006GA/GB]]'s board. :Per the GPL source, this device is using BCM6348 (presumably BCM6348S).
Addtional specifications, per '''TRENDnet''''s datasheet, are below... *Dimensions: [[Dimensions::175 mm x 130 mm x 30 mm]] *Weight: [[Weight::255 g]]
Default settings are per '''TRENDnet''''s manual. :The used OUI is per '''WiGLE'''.
